		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Try one of the tile editors here.
<br /><a href="http://nesdev.com/#PCGraphics" class="postlink">http://nesdev.com/#PCGraphics</a>
<br />
<br />The graphics for the sprites will be in the CHR file (or whatever someone names it, if they use CHR-RAM).  But the actual organization of the tiles (placement, colors) is determined by the program.

		

		</td>
