		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, I almost always have trouble converting graphics too.  Seems like every converter to CHR has it's own way of dealing with the colors.
<br />
<br />YY-CHR is very nice, I haven't tried using it like Celius said, but I bet that'll work well.  The way I've had the best luck with converting graphics is by using Tile Molester.  Just be sure it goes to the right format, because Tile Molester has a lot of options, heheh.

		

		</td>
