	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />CHR graphics are 4 colors, and the first of those is transparent.  The actual colors used are defined seperately when it's displayed on NES.  You can save your palette in the PPU's format with "save palette set file" in YY-CHR.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


