		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Celius wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I always make sure it's 3F</div>
<br />
<br />$0F is the more 'typical' black and is used by most games.  But $3F is probably fine.
<br />
<br />Staying away from $0D is very good advice.

		

